            <h1 class="display-4">This Website is in Beta!</h1>
            <p class="lead">That means its very new and most likely very buggy...</p>
            <hr class="my-4" />
            <p>
                If you encounter problems, <strong>please</strong> email
                <a href="mailto:hanna.flores@unt.edu">hanna.flores@unt.edu</a>
                or fill out <a href="/bugreport">this form</a>
                with what happened, what you were doing when it happened, and what time it happened at. Thank you very
                much!
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/bugreport" role="button">Submit a bug report?</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="mailto:hanna.flores@unt.edu" role="button">Or send me an email?</a>
