                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2>3D Printing</h2>
                            <p>
                                The Spark Makerspace has an army of 3D printers in both locations to print models for
                                our patrons! Just submit your models through this website, and pick up your models in 5
                                to 7 business days. Prints for classes are completely free, just make sure to tell us
                                the class and professor in the notes when you submit your files. Otherwise, we only
                                charge $1 per hour of print time.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                We offer prints in PLA and ABS in a wide variety of colors, just let us know what you
                                would like in the submission form.
                            </p>
                            <p><a href="">3D Printing Submission Process</a></p>

                            <a role="button" class="btn btn-primary" href="/submit">Submit 3D Print</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
